=head1 DESCRIPTION

Contains the details for a document that was ingested or deleted.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> DataSourceId => Str

The identifier of the data source connected to the knowledge base that
the document was ingested into or deleted from.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Identifier => L<Paws::BedrockAgent::DocumentIdentifier>

Contains information that identifies the document.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> KnowledgeBaseId => Str

The identifier of the knowledge base that the document was ingested
into or deleted from.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Status => Str

The ingestion status of the document. The following statuses are
possible:

=over

=item *

STARTED E<ndash> You submitted the ingestion job containing the
document.

=item *

PENDING E<ndash> The document is waiting to be ingested.

=item *

IN_PROGRESS E<ndash> The document is being ingested.

=item *

INDEXED E<ndash> The document was successfully indexed.

=item *

PARTIALLY_INDEXED E<ndash> The document was partially indexed.

=item *

METADATA_PARTIALLY_INDEXED E<ndash> You submitted metadata for an
existing document and it was partially indexed.

=item *

METADATA_UPDATE_FAILED E<ndash> You submitted a metadata update for an
existing document but it failed.

=item *

FAILED E<ndash> The document failed to be ingested.

=item *

NOT_FOUND E<ndash> The document wasn't found.

=item *

IGNORED E<ndash> The document was ignored during ingestion.

=item *

DELETING E<ndash> You submitted the delete job containing the document.

=item *

DELETE_IN_PROGRESS E<ndash> The document is being deleted.

=back



=head2 StatusReason => Str

The reason for the status. Appears alongside the status C<IGNORED>.


=head2 UpdatedAt => Str

The date and time at which the document was last updated.



